title: Earthquake close to Mammoth Lakes, California
text:
Earthquake close to Mammoth Lakes, California   
Aug 22, 2015 eTN   
A 4.0-magnitude earthquake struck about 11 miles east of Mammoth Lakes, California around 6.50 am. This was reported by USGS. 
No reports of damages or injuries are known at this time
